data.description: Chelsea Ct, a location in Woodbridge where homes rarely come on the market. This Eastgate model has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, Den/office, unfinished bonus room/4th bedroom, dining area, courtyard entry garage and is located on a cul-de-sac sitting on nearly a half acre. This home boasts hardwood floors, a fabulous eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances, newer water heater. This backyard is great for gatherings or just enjoying the covered patio overlooking the wooded views. Start making your vacation living part of your everyday lifestyle.
